reviewText: For some reason, when I ripped the disc to my computer, the audio sounds like a poorer quality when I play it. The sound is really overblown and so unnecessarily loud that it's almost static-y. The disc plays fine in CD players, though.
That is simply it, it won't play on all of my CD players and DVD players. The album itself is phenomenal! It's a true sequel to "I Get Wet" and one of the funnest albums of all time!
